        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "text": "It is impossible to imagine any project without data. Tones of effort are spent to solve the problem of retrieving / grouping / filtering / sorting / visualizing data. Everything becomes even worse when it is necessary to implement the pattern of data lazy-loading, add some folding logic, different strategies of selecting elements with children nodes, etc.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {},
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "text": "To solve these and other problems ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "object": "text",
            "text": "Datasources",
            "marks": [
              {
                "object": "mark",
                "type": "uui-richTextEditor-code",
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "object": "text",
            "text": " were developed. They are kind of black boxes, which encapsulates complex solutions to various problems, providing simple abstraction.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {},
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "text",
            "text": "Problems data sources are solving:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "data": {},
        "nodes": [
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "data": {},
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "block",
                "type": "list-item-child",
                "data": {},
                "nodes": [
                  {
                    "object": "text",
                    "text": "converting data to renderable rows with multiple handlers (folding, selecting, focusing, clicking) based on the configuration;",
                    "marks": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "data": {},
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "block",
                "type": "list-item-child",
                "data": {},
                "nodes": [
                  {
                    "object": "text",
                    "text": "providing the abstraction over data fetching strategy; it doesn't matter if Datasource is fetching data from an array, some endpoint, or partially loading tonnes of records;",
                    "marks": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "data": {},
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "block",
                "type": "list-item-child",
                "data": {},
                "nodes": [
                  {
                    "object": "text",
                    "text": "implementing various selecting records strategies, such as picking a record only or with its children implicitly or explicitly;",
                    "marks": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "data": {},
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "block",
                "type": "list-item-child",
                "data": {},
                "nodes": [
                  {
                    "object": "text",
                    "text": "configuring renderable rows;",
                    "marks": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "object": "block",
            "type": "list-item",
            "data": {},
            "nodes": [
              {
                "object": "block",
                "type": "list-item-child",
                "data": {},
                "nodes": [
                  {
                    "object": "text",
                    "text": "enabling the possibility to filter/search over data, and sort data, no matter which fetching strategy is provided;",
                    "marks": []
                  }
                ]
